data.description: NEW PRICE! Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with beautiful woodwork, built-ins, and hardwood floors. There is a nice deep backyard, carport, and shed. Enter through the back door into a mudroom with the laundry area and bathroom conveniently close to the entrance. The kitchen is well designed with a formal dining room adjacent to it. The living room is open to the dining room. 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom are on the second floor. There is a walk-up attic. The owner will not make any repairs based on a home inspection or appraisal.
